Author: Robert Pyke
Last Updated: 2009/11/24

URI Map (API)

GETS:
/
    Display a home page


######### /my/ ############################################

/my/profile
    Display the user's profile, and allow for editing

/my/quizzes
    Display the user's quizzes, and allow for links to modification, removal, etc.

###########################################################


######### /quiz ###########################################

/quiz/create_quiz
    Display a form to add a quiz

/quiz/take/[quiz_id]
    Do a quiz

/quiz/profile/[quiz_id]
    Show the stats for a quiz

/user/profile/[user_id]
    Show the stats for the user

/quiz/modify/[quiz_id]
    Allows the author of a quiz to add questions, remove questions, etc.

###########################################################

/login
    Handle login redirect

# txt gets (API)
/txt/quiz/quiz_list
    Print the list of available quizzes

POST:
/post/quiz/create_quiz
    Store the newly created quiz in the database

